    "# PEFT Benchmark Notebook: LoRA vs. Laplace-LoRA vs. Causal Fine-Tuning\n",
    "## Production-Ready GLUE Evaluation Suite\n",
    "\n",
    "**Target Tasks**: MRPC · SST-2 · QNLI (GLUE Benchmark)\n",
    "\n",
    "| Method | Core Idea | Uncertainty | Key Tech |\n",
    "|--------|-----------|-------------|----------|\n",
    "| **Baseline LoRA** | Low-rank adapters | ❌ None | $W' = W_0 + \\frac{\\alpha}{r}BA$ |\n",
    "| **Laplace-LoRA** | Gaussian posterior | ✅ Calibrated | K-FAC Hessian approx |\n",
    "| **Causal FT** | Do-calculus reweighting | ✳️ Structural | Backdoor adjustment |\n",
    "\n",
    "**Metrics**: Accuracy, F1, NLL, ECE, Latency (ms/sample)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Environments**: Google Colab ✅ | Local Git Clone ✅ | Shared `src/` runtime ✅"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "523c8fba",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Colab Quick Start (Recovery-First)\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Save your HF token in Colab Secrets as HF_TOKEN (Settings > Secrets > New Secret).\n",
    "2. Run Cell 2 (Bootstrap) and Cell 3 (Environment).\n",
    "3. Run Cell 4 (Install) and Cell 5 (Runtime Env).\n",
    "4. Run Cell 6 (Imports), Cell 7 (Config), Cell 8 (Data), and Cell 10 (Utilities).\n",
    "5. Start any experiment cell; each task auto-saves checkpoints and run state.\n",
    "6. If runtime disconnects, reconnect and run cells in order again; training resumes from latest checkpoint.\n",
    "\n",
    "Recommended first pass: LoRA baseline only, then Laplace, then Causal."
   ]
