    "---\n",
    "## Section 3B — Executable Notebook Update Plan Checklist\n",
    "\n",
    "This section turns the plan into executable gates.\n",
    "\n",
    "Run the next code cell before starting Method 1.\n",
    "\n",
    "Checklist gates enforced:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. UV tooling available in runtime (Colab or local).\n",
    "2. Supported tasks only (`mrpc`, `sst2`, `qnli`).\n",
    "3. Positive causal scheduling parameters (`total_causal_budget`, `async_max_steps`, `apply_interval`).\n",
    "4. `apply_interval <= async_max_steps`.\n",
    "5. Device/runtime metadata captured for audit.\n",
    "\n",
    "Status tracking policy:\n",
    "\n",
    "- Each method-task run writes a checklist status entry.\n",
    "- Fail-closed methods (Laplace, Causal) must mark `passed` for all tasks.\n",
    "- Final checklist summary reports pass/fail counts and pending tasks."
   ]
  },
